// Manual lexicon, to convert SRL to AMR output
// Format is:
// AMR	SRL	LEMMAS...
// AMR roles start with semicolon (:), whereas concepts don't
// If LEMMAS is empty, the interpretation will be used for all words with that category. Otherwise, it will only be used for the specified words (using their lower-cased lemmas).

